name: ptitprince
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ptitprince" %}
{% set version = "0.2.5" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/ptitprince-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1b3dbac736f1180d865b9ae2508f2ce59769fc85800cbee120d2a3cbc67c6368

build:
  number: 3
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - cython
    - matplotlib-base
    - numpy >=1.13
    - pyhamcrest >=1.9.0
    - python
    - scipy
    - seaborn >=0.10

test:
  imports:
    - ptitprince
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: http://github.com/pog87/PtitPrince
  summary: A Python implementation of Rainclouds, originally on R, ggplot2. Written on top of seaborn.
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pog87
    - sappelhoff
